          "date": "2014-08-25 20:01:04.000000000",
          "tz": -300
        },
        "subject": "LU-5541: lustrapi: only export the necessary symbols",
        "message": "LU-5541: lustrapi: only export the necessary symbols\n\nBy default, all kind of symbol are exported from the library (dump,\nlibcfs_ukuc_start, l_ioctl, set_ioctl_dump, ...), which may create\nexternal conflicts. Use the linker version-script options to only\nexport the symbols we care about.\n\nOnly the symbols declared in the global section of liblustreapi.map\nwill be seen by applications.\n\nChange-Id: Iac1b49ef19ead2f5229151c1a404be268bf05812\nSigned-off-by: frank zago <fzago@cray.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
